data.description: MOVE IN READY! Many Updates and Extras. Home is in a great location walking distance to Butcher-Greene Elementary. Off-Street 3 car deep driveway. Great looking refinished hardwood flooring throughout most of the Main Floor. Lots of windows. Living room opens to Kitchen/Dining area. Kitchen offers tile counter tops, gas stove, lazy susan, and stainless steel refrigerator. Built-in by back door (big, open window door for more light in Kitchen area). Smart thermostat. Full Bath in Basement. Exterior has been well maintained and recently painted. Roof looks to be in good condition. SO MANY EXTRAS...SIX-Foot tall chain link fence around Backyard. Home backs to green space with access to the John Anderson Sports Park. Big mature trees and Shed in back. GOOGLE FIBER available!!! Solid foundation with steel beam reinforcement. Radon Mitigation System in place. Just pack your bags and move in. JUST MINUTES from all amenities in Belton and Raymore area, as well as all the great stuff available in Grandview. FINALLY a decent Home under the 200k range. Seller provides Home Warranty.
